<%- include('../partials/head') %>

<body class="min-h-screen w-full">
    <header class="landing-art flex flex-col px-8 justify-center items-end h-screen w-full bg-gray-100">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-end">
            <%- include('../partials/brand') %>
            <em class="text-base text-gray-400 capitalize mt-1 font-semibold">
                a place for cinephiles
            </em>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">
                mov·ie
            </h2>
            <span class="text-gray-400 font-semibold">
                /ˈmo͞ovē/
            </span>
            <em class="text-gray-700 text-base font-serif capitalize">
                a motion picture; a movie.
            </em>
            <em class="text-gray-700 text-base font-serif break-all">
                movies are considered as an art or industry.
            </em>
            <a href="#about" class="inline-block capitalize font-light py-1 px-4 mt-8 bg-gray-700 text-gray-300 w-max z-10 rounded shadow-md transition-all transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg">
                learn more
            </a>
        </div>

    </header>
    
    <main id="about" class="landing-art h-screen w-full bg-gray-100 py-12 px-4 flex flex-col justify-start">
        <h2 class="text-3xl capitalize font-extrabold text-gray-500 border-b-2 border-red-600 w-max mx-auto mb-2">
            watch good movies
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base italic max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Life is too short to watch all the movies ever made. Why not watch movies based on reviews? Search the movie you are thinking of watching. Read the Moovey reviewer's ratings for a movie. Watch it if you think it's worth your time.
        </p>
        <a href="/blogs" class="capitalize text-sm border-b-2 border-transparent block mx-auto my-6 w-max font-semibold transition-all text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 hover:border-red-700 focus:text-red-700 focus:border-red-700">
            see reviews
        </a>

        <h2 class="text-3xl capitalize font-extrabold text-gray-500 border-b-2 border-red-600 w-max mx-auto my-2">
            be a reviewer
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base italic text-center">
            Watch a movie. Write what you like/dislike about the movie. Submit your rating. Voila!
        </p>
        <blockquote class="my-4 rounded-md shadow-lg overflow-hidden max-w-prose mx-auto p-4 flex flex-col items-start border-l-8 border-red-600 bg-white">
            <div class="flex jusity-start">
                <sup class="text-2xl text-gray-400">
                    &#10077;
                </sup>
                <em class="font-semibold mx-2 text-gray-500">
                    Frankly, my dear, I don't give a damn.
                </em>    
                <sup class="text-2xl text-gray-400">
                    &#10078;
                </sup>
            </div>
            <span class="self-end text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400">
                &mdash; Gone with the Wind (1939)
            </span>
        </blockquote>
        <h2 class="text-2xl capitalize font-light text-gray-500 w-max mx-auto my-2">
            and so much more ... 
        </h2>
        <a href="/login"
           class="uppercase text-lg block mx-auto mt-8 w-max font-semibold transition-all text-gray-400 bg-gray-800 py-2 px-4 shadow-md rounded-md hover:text-gray-200 hover:shadow-2xl transform hover:-translate-y-1">
            join now
        </a>
    </main>

    <footer class="p-8 flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-gray-900">
        <div class="my-8 flex justify-center items-center flex-col text-gray-400">
            <strong class="text-xl">
                Moovey
            </strong>
            <small class="text-xs text-gray-500 w-5/6 text-center my-2">
                this website is purely for non-commercial usage. you can read reviews without having an account. to write a movie review, rate a movie review etc you need to have an account.   
                <br>
                <em class="text-gray-400">
                    Photo by Kris Lucas from Pexels
                </em>
            </small>
            <h5 class="capitalize text-xs text-gray-200">
                created by sounak mukherjee
            </h5>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>